    "faq_with_image_m73Xra": {
      "type": "faq-with-image",
      "blocks": {
        "accordion_GhRGXt": {
          "type": "accordion",
          "settings": {
            "accordion_header": "What happens after I place my order online?",
            "open_by_default": false,
            "text": "<p>Once you finalise your design and place your order, our master goldsmiths in Chichester carefully review the specifications. We source your chosen diamond, cast the precious metal, and meticulously hand-finish your piece. The entire crafting process typically takes 4-6 weeks.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "accordion_HmVJLJ": {
          "type": "accordion",
          "settings": {
            "accordion_header": "Can I design something completely from scratch?",
            "open_by_default": false,
            "text": "<p>While the online studio offers thousands of combinations, if you have a completely unique vision that cannot be built in the app, we recommend our <a href=\"/pages/bespoke-jewellery-designs\" title=\"Bespoke Jewellery Designs\">Bespoke Design Service</a>. You can book an appointment to work from a blank canvas with our designers.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "accordion_xFhTbU": {
          "type": "accordion",
          "settings": {
            "accordion_header": "Are the 3D renders an accurate representation?",
            "open_by_default": false,
            "text": "<p>Yes, our 3D technology provides highly accurate, photorealistic renders of how your final piece will look, proportioned perfectly to your chosen diamond and ring size.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "accordion_pxHnfz": {
          "type": "accordion",
          "settings": {
            "accordion_header": "Is my online bespoke design guaranteed?",
            "open_by_default": false,
            "text": "<p>Absolutely. Every piece crafted by Griffin & Co, whether designed in-store or via our online studio, comes with a comprehensive guarantee of craftsmanship and a complimentary first-year check and clean in our workshop.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        }
      },
